モジュール io.helidon.http.http2

インタフェースHttp2Frame<T extends Http2Flag>

型パラメータ:
T - サポートされるフラグのタイプ
既知のすべての実装クラス:
Http2Continuation, Http2DataFrame, Http2GoAway, Http2Ping, Http2Priority, Http2RstStream, Http2Settings, Http2WindowUpdate
public sealed interface Http2Frame<T extends Http2Flag> permits Http2Continuation, Http2DataFrame, Http2GoAway, Http2Ping, Http2Priority, Http2RstStream, Http2Settings, Http2WindowUpdate
HTTP/2 frame.
